title: Anders Holm
itunes:title: Anders Holm
description:
Anders Holm (WORKAHOLICS, THE MINDY PROJECT, GAME OVER, MAN!) is our guest today making everyone laugh until they cry.  He and Whitney talk about mung diving, his extra tooth, and Whitney's first impression of him (not good).  We also hear about the first time they met--it involves a finger in the butt.  Anders' new show INVENTING ANNA is streaming on Netflix now and listen to his podcast THIS IS IMPORTANT wherever you get your pods.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
